### Cloud Service Models

* **IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service)** – Provides virtualized infrastructure (VMs, storage, networking); users manage the OS and applications.
* **PaaS (Platform as a Service)** – Provides a platform to build and deploy applications without managing the underlying infrastructure.
* **SaaS (Software as a Service)** – Delivers ready-to-use software over the internet; users access it through a browser.

